Introducing AI Lawyer & Judge – An Indian Legal System AI Assistant**
This project uses Google Gemini 2.5 Flash and Python to analyze legal scenarios **strictly according to Indian laws** and generate **precise legal consequences in JSON format**.

No more vague legal answers — get **exact punishments, severity levels, and compensation details** instantly!

###🔹 Features**

✅ Analyzes legal cases as per **Indian Penal Code (IPC)**
✅ Returns structured **JSON output** for easy integration into apps
✅ Identifies punishment type: death penalty, life imprisonment, jail, fine, etc.
✅ Calculates severity: Severe / Moderate / Mild
✅ Generates compensation amounts where applicable
✅ Built using **Python + Gemini AI API**

